data.description: ***OPEN HOUSE 1/14/23 FROM 2:00-5:00***   Welcome home to this amazing 4 bedroom, 3 bath house located in Easley. The home sits on 1.53 acres with an additional 1.93 acres next to it (tax map #5130-18-42-8175). As you pull up to the home, you'll notice the lovely wrap around porch. Once you enter through the front door, you will come into the living room. You will get all the open concept feels with the living room, dining room, and kitchen right there. As you turn left, you'll have your first bedroom or office followed by the spacious Master Bedroom. In the master bathroom, you have a double sink with a jetted tub and shower. As you go into the huge walk-in closet it is divided into two sides with plenty of room. Upstairs you will find 2 additional rooms. Coming off the kitchen, there is a very nice sunroom with plenty of sunshine coming through. Connected to the sunroom, is the 2 car garage with a huge upstairs that could be used for storage or made into another bonus room. Outside you have an enormous 30x20 deck that overlooks the above ground pool/backyard. It is the perfect place to have friends and family over. Off to the side of the deck, there is an additional workshop that can be utilized. At the back of the property, there is plenty of exploration along with a creek. This property has so much potential to offer. You must see it to appreciate this home. Schedule your showing today!
